710 Q_EXPORT intptr_t vmMain(intptr_t command, intptr_t arg0, intptr_t arg1, intptr_t arg2, intptr_t arg3, intptr_t arg4, intptr_t arg5, intptr_t arg6)
711 {
712  switch (command)
713  {
714  case GAME_INIT:
715  {
716  float time = trap_Milliseconds();
717  Com_Printf(S_COLOR_MDGREY "Initializing Legacy game " S_COLOR_GREEN ETLEGACY_VERSION "\n");
718 #ifdef FEATURE_OMNIBOT
719 
720  Bot_Interface_InitHandles();
721 #endif
722  G_InitGame(arg0, arg1, arg2, arg3, arg4);
723  G_Printf("Game Initialization completed in %.2f seconds.\n", ((float)trap_Milliseconds() - time) / 1000.f);
724 #ifdef FEATURE_OMNIBOT
725 
726  time = trap_Milliseconds();
727 
728  if (!Bot_Interface_Init())
729  {
730  G_Printf(S_COLOR_RED "Unable to Initialize Omni-Bot.\n");
731  }
732 
733  if (g_OmniBotEnable.integer >= 1)
734  {
735  // that's the only way to print the used bot version atm
736  trap_SendConsoleCommand(EXEC_APPEND, va("%s", "bot version\n"));
737 
738  G_Printf(S_COLOR_GREEN "Omni-Bot Initialization completed in %.2f seconds.\n", ((float)trap_Milliseconds() - time) / 1000.f);
739  }
740 #endif
741  }
742  return 0;
743  case GAME_SHUTDOWN:
744  G_ShutdownGame(arg0);
745  return 0;
746  case GAME_CLIENT_CONNECT:
747  return (intptr_t)ClientConnect(arg0, arg1, arg2);
748  case GAME_CLIENT_THINK:
749  ClientThink(arg0);
750  return 0;
751  case GAME_CLIENT_USERINFO_CHANGED:
752  ClientUserinfoChanged(arg0);
753  return 0;
754  case GAME_CLIENT_DISCONNECT:
755  ClientDisconnect(arg0);
756  return 0;
757  case GAME_CLIENT_BEGIN:
758  ClientBegin(arg0);
759  return 0;
760  case GAME_CLIENT_COMMAND:
761  ClientCommand(arg0);
762  return 0;
763  case GAME_RUN_FRAME:
764  G_RunFrame(arg0);
765 #ifdef FEATURE_OMNIBOT
766  Bot_Interface_Update();
767 #endif
768  return 0;
769  case GAME_CONSOLE_COMMAND:
770  return ConsoleCommand();
771  case GAME_SNAPSHOT_CALLBACK:
772  return G_SnapshotCallback(arg0, arg1);
773  case GAME_MESSAGERECEIVED:
774  return -1;
775  default:
776  G_Printf("Bad game export type: %ld\n", (long int) command);
777  break;
778  }
779 
780  return -1;
781 }

878 qboolean G_EmplacedGunIsMountable(gentity_t *ent, gentity_t *other)
879 {
880  if (Q_stricmp(ent->classname, "misc_mg42") && Q_stricmp(ent->classname, "misc_aagun"))
881  {
882  return qfalse;
883  }
884 
885  if (!other->client)
886  {
887  return qfalse;
888  }
889 
890  if (GetWeaponTableData(other->client->ps.weapon)->type & (WEAPON_TYPE_SCOPED | WEAPON_TYPE_SET))
891  {
892  return qfalse;
893  }
894 
895  if (other->client->ps.pm_flags & PMF_DUCKED)
896  {
897  return qfalse;
898  }
899 
900  if (other->client->ps.persistant[PERS_HWEAPON_USE])
901  {
902  return qfalse;
903  }
904 
905  if (ent->r.currentOrigin[2] - other->r.currentOrigin[2] >= 40)
906  {
907  return qfalse;
908  }
909 
910  if (ent->r.currentOrigin[2] - other->r.currentOrigin[2] < 0)
911  {
912  return qfalse;
913  }
914 
915  if (ent->s.frame != 0)
916  {
917  return qfalse;
918  }
919 
920  if (ent->active)
921  {
922  return qfalse;
923  }
924 
925  if (other->client->ps.weaponDelay)
926  {
927  return qfalse;
928  }
929 
930  if (other->client->ps.grenadeTimeLeft)
931  {
932  return qfalse;
933  }
934 
935  if (infront(ent, other))
936  {
937  return qfalse;
938  }
939 
940  return qtrue;
941 }

990 void G_CheckForCursorHints(gentity_t *ent)
991 {
992  vec3_t forward, right, up, offset, end;
993  trace_t *tr;
994  float dist;
995  gentity_t *checkEnt, *traceEnt = 0;
996  playerState_t *ps;
997  static int hintValMax = 255; // Breakable damage indicator can wrap when the entity has a lot of health
998  int hintType, hintDist, hintVal;
999  qboolean zooming;
1000  int trace_contents;
1001  int numOfIgnoredEnts = 0;
1002 
1003  if (!ent->client)
1004  {
1005  return;
1006  }
1007 
1008  ps = &ent->client->ps;
1009 
1010  zooming = (qboolean)(ps->eFlags & EF_ZOOMING);
1011 
1012  AngleVectors(ps->viewangles, forward, right, up);
1013 
1014  VectorCopy(ps->origin, offset);
1015  offset[2] += ps->viewheight;
1016 
1017  // lean
1018  if (ps->leanf != 0.f)
1019  {
1020  VectorMA(offset, ps->leanf, right, offset);
1021  }
1022 
1023  if (zooming)
1024  {
1025  VectorMA(offset, CH_MAX_DIST_ZOOM, forward, end);
1026  }
1027  else
1028  {
1029  VectorMA(offset, CH_MAX_DIST, forward, end);
1030  }
1031 
1032  tr = &ps->serverCursorHintTrace;
1033 
1034  trace_contents = (CONTENTS_TRIGGER | CONTENTS_SOLID | CONTENTS_MISSILECLIP | CONTENTS_BODY | CONTENTS_CORPSE);
1035  trap_Trace(tr, offset, NULL, NULL, end, ps->clientNum, trace_contents);
1036 
1037  // reset all
1038  hintType = ps->serverCursorHint = HINT_NONE;
1039  hintVal = ps->serverCursorHintVal = 0;
1040 
1041  dist = VectorDistanceSquared(offset, tr->endpos);
1042 
1043  if (zooming)
1044  {
1045  hintDist = CH_MAX_DIST_ZOOM;
1046  }
1047  else
1048  {
1049  hintDist = CH_MAX_DIST;
1050  }
1051 
1052  if (ps->stats[STAT_PLAYER_CLASS] == PC_COVERTOPS)
1053  {
1054  if (ent->client->landmineSpottedTime && level.time - ent->client->landmineSpottedTime < 500)
1055  {
1056  ps->serverCursorHint = HINT_LANDMINE;
1057  ps->serverCursorHintVal = ent->client->landmineSpotted ? ent->client->landmineSpotted->count2 : 0;
1058  return;
1059  }
1060  }
1061

1689 void G_FindTeams(void)
1690 {
1691  gentity_t *e, *e2;
1692  int i, j;
1693  int c = 0, c2 = 0;
1694 
1695  for (i = MAX_CLIENTS, e = g_entities + i ; i < level.num_entities ; i++, e++)
1696  {
1697  if (!e->inuse)
1698  {
1699  continue;
1700  }
1701 
1702  if (!e->team)
1703  {
1704  continue;
1705  }
1706 
1707  if (e->flags & FL_TEAMSLAVE)
1708  {
1709  continue;
1710  }
1711 
1712  c++;
1713  c2++;
1714  for (j = i + 1, e2 = e + 1 ; j < level.num_entities ; j++, e2++)
1715  {
1716  if (!e2->inuse)
1717  {
1718  continue;
1719  }
1720  if (!e2->team)
1721  {
1722  continue;
1723  }
1724  if (e2->flags & FL_TEAMSLAVE)
1725  {
1726  continue;
1727  }
1728  if (!strcmp(e->team, e2->team))
1729  {
1730  c2++;
1731  e2->teamchain = e->teamchain;

2832 int QDECL SortRanks(const void *a, const void *b)
2833 {
2834  gclient_t *ca = &level.clients[*(const int *)a];
2835  gclient_t *cb = &level.clients[*(const int *)b];
2836 
2837  // sort special clients last
2838  if (ca->sess.spectatorClient < 0)
2839  {
2840  return 1;
2841  }
2842  if (cb->sess.spectatorClient < 0)
2843  {
2844  return -1;
2845  }
2846 
2847  // then connecting clients
2848  if (ca->pers.connected == CON_CONNECTING)
2849  {
2850  return 1;
2851  }
2852  if (cb->pers.connected == CON_CONNECTING)
2853  {
2854  return -1;
2855  }
2856 
2857  // then spectators
2858  if (ca->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR && cb->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR)
2859  {
2860  if (ca->sess.spectatorTime < cb->sess.spectatorTime)
2861  {
2862  return -1;
2863  }
2864  if (ca->sess.spectatorTime > cb->sess.spectatorTime)
2865  {
2866  return 1;
2867  }
2868  return 0;
2869  }
2870  if (ca->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR)
2871  {
2872  return 1;
2873  }
2874  if (cb->sess.sessionTeam == TEAM_SPECTATOR)
2875  {
2876  return -1;
2877  }
2878 
2879  if (g_gametype.integer == GT_WOLF_LMS)
2880  {
2881  // then sort by score
2882  if (ca->ps.persistant[PERS_SCORE] > cb->ps.persistant[PERS_SCORE])
2883  {
2884  return -1;
2885  }
2886  if (ca->ps.persistant[PERS_SCORE] < cb->ps.persistant[PERS_SCORE])
2887  {
2888  return 1;
2889  }
2890  }
2891  else
2892  {
2893  int i, totalXP[2];
2894 
2895  for (totalXP[0] = totalXP[1] = 0, i = 0; i < SK_NUM_SKILLS; i++)
2896  {
2897  totalXP[0] += ca->sess.skillpoints[i];
2898  totalXP[1] += cb->sess.skillpoints[i];
2899  }
2900 
2901  if (!((g_gametype.integer == GT_WOLF_CAMPAIGN && (g_campaigns[level.currentCampaign].current != 0 && !level.newCampaign)) ||
2902  (g_gametype.integer == GT_WOLF_LMS && g_currentRound.integer != 0)))
2903  {
2904  // current map XPs only
2905  totalXP[0] -= ca->sess.startxptotal;
2906  totalXP[1] -= cb->sess.startxptotal;
2907  }
2908 
2909  // then sort by xp
2910  if (totalXP[0] > totalXP[1])
2911  {
2912  return -1;
2913  }
2914  if (totalXP[0] < totalXP[1])
2915  {
2916  return 1;
2917  }
2918  }
2919  return 0;
2920 }
2921 
2925 void etpro_PlayerInfo(void)
2926 {
2927  //128 bits
2928  char playerinfo[MAX_CLIENTS + 1];
2929  gentity_t *e = &g_entities[0];
2930  team_t playerteam;
2931  int i;
2932  int lastclient = -1;
2933 
2934  Com_Memset(playerinfo, 0, sizeof(playerinfo));
2935 
2936  for (i = 0; i < MAX_CLIENTS; i++, e++)
2937  {
2938  if (e->client == NULL || e->client->pers.connected == CON_DISCONNECTED)
2939  {
2940  playerinfo[i] = '-';
2941  continue;
2942  }
2943 
2944  // keep track of highest connected/connecting client
2945  lastclient = i;
2946 
2947  if (e->inuse == qfalse)
2948  {
2949  playerteam = 0;
2950  }
2951  else
2952  {

3335  // A real shuffle ...
3336  // This way not always the same maps will be on top of the list.

3338  // Note: They will never see more than 32 maps in the list (to vote for).
3339  {
3340  char shuffledNames[64][128];
3341  qboolean shuffled[64] = { 0 };
3342  int j = 0;

3344  // shuffle the complete list:
3345  // Backup the list, erase the list, shuffle names, fill the list again..

3360  ++j;
3361  bspptrTmp += strlen(bspptrTmp) + 1;
3362  }
3363  maxMaps = j;

3367  // I know, perhaps this is a silly way of shuffling the list,
3368  // but at least the rest of code stays the same.
3369  Com_Memset(bspNames, 0, sizeof(bspNames));
3370  bspptrTmp = bspptr;
3371  for (i = 0; i < maxMaps; ++i)
3372  {
3373  int r = rand() % maxMaps;
3374 
3375  while (shuffled[r])
3376  {
3377  --r;

3380  r = maxMaps - 1;
3381  }
3382  }

3386  }

4308 void CheckVote(void)
4309 {

4313  {
4314  return;

4333

4335  + level.voteInfo.voteNo);

4342

4354  else
4355  {
4356  total = level.voteInfo.numVotingClients;

4360  {

4381

4383  if ((g_voting.integer & VOTEF_NO_POPULIST_PENALTY))

4393  }

5086 void G_RunFrame(int levelTime)
5087 {
5088  int i, msec;
5089 
5090  // if we are waiting for the level to restart, do nothing
5091  if (level.restarted)
5092  {
5093  return;
5094  }
5095 
5096  // workaround for q3 bug
5097  // levelTime will start over when the timelimit expires on dual objective maps.
5098  if (level.previousTime > level.time)
5099  {
5100  level.overTime = level.previousTime;
5101  }
5102 
5103  levelTime = levelTime + level.overTime;
5104 
5105  // Handling of pause offsets
5106  if (level.match_pause == PAUSE_NONE)
5107  {
5108  level.timeCurrent = levelTime - level.timeDelta;
5109  }
5110  else
5111  {
5112  level.timeDelta = levelTime - level.timeCurrent;
5113  if ((level.time % 500) == 0)
5114  {
5115  // FIXME: set a PAUSE cs and let the client adjust their local starttimes
5116  // instead of this spam
5117  trap_SetConfigstring(CS_LEVEL_START_TIME, va("%i", level.startTime + level.timeDelta));
5118  }
5119  }
5120 
5121  level.frameTime = trap_Milliseconds();
5122 
5123  level.framenum++;
5124  level.previousTime = level.time;
5125  level.time = levelTime;
5126 
5127  msec = level.time - level.previousTime;
5128 
5129  level.axisAirstrikeCounter -= msec;
5130  level.alliedAirstrikeCounter -= msec;
5131  level.axisArtilleryCounter -= msec;
5132  level.alliedArtilleryCounter -= msec;
5133 
5134  if (level.axisAirstrikeCounter < 0)
5135  {
5136  level.axisAirstrikeCounter = 0;
5137  }
5138  if (level.alliedAirstrikeCounter < 0)
5139  {
5140  level.alliedAirstrikeCounter = 0;
5141  }
5142 
5143  if (level.axisArtilleryCounter < 0)
5144  {
5145  level.axisArtilleryCounter = 0;
5146  }
5147  if (level.alliedArtilleryCounter < 0)
5148  {
5149  level.alliedArtilleryCounter = 0;
5150  }
5151 
5152  // get any cvar changes
5153  G_UpdateCvars();
5154 
5155  G_ConfigCheckLocked();
5156 
5157  for (i = 0; i < level.num_entities; i++)
5158  {
5159  g_entities[i].runthisframe = qfalse;
5160  }
5161 
5162  // go through all allocated objects
5163  for (i = 0; i < level.num_entities; i++)
5164  {
5165  G_RunEntity(&g_entities[i], msec);
5166  }
5167 
5168  for (i = 0; i < level.numConnectedClients; i++)
5169  {
5170  ClientEndFrame(&g_entities[level.sortedClients[i]]);
5171  }
5172 
5173  CheckWolfMP();
5174 
5175  // see if it is time to end the level
5176  CheckExitRules();
5177 
5178  // update to team status?
5179  CheckTeamStatus();
5180 
5181  // cancel vote if timed out
5182  CheckVote();
5183 
5184  // for tracking changes
5185  CheckCvars();
5186 
5187  G_UpdateTeamMapData();
5188 
5189  if (level.gameManager)
5190  {
5191  level.gameManager->s.otherEntityNum = team_maxLandmines.integer - G_CountTeamLandmines(TEAM_AXIS);
5192  level.gameManager->s.otherEntityNum2 = team_maxLandmines.integer - G_CountTeamLandmines(TEAM_ALLIES);
5193  }
5194 #ifdef FEATURE_LUA
5195  G_LuaHook_RunFrame(levelTime);
5196 #endif
5197 }
